summary: A note on Dan and Phil’s current Hiatus:
body:
A note on Dan and Phil’s current Hiatus:

Okay so I discovered Dan and Phil pretty recently, almost a year and a half ago. Dan’s channel especially brought me out of a big bout of depression and I appreciated that so much you can’t even imagine. And then I discovered the gaming channel and Phil’s and binged the FUCK out of everything. And even them as people, like real GENUINE people is absolutely amazing and they are just an astonishing pair of people that support so many important things in this fucked up society of ours and I’m so grateful kids like me have some source to turn to. This is why it upsets me soooo much to hear all these theories and hate that Dan and Phil are getting from part of the Phandom. Yes Dan hasn’t posted in abt a year. Yes Phil has different type of content. Yes they’re changing, and yes they may be quitting YouTube or moving apart or whatever. But they are HUMAN BEINGS and human beings CHANGE. And yes, I’m upset that they’ll probably be leaving. They are both the people I turn to when I can’t get out of the bed in the morning. I wait on my phone, refreshing the YouTube app just so I can watch a 5 min video that will honestly bring my day from 0-100 somehow. So I get where everyone is coming from, but please just keep in mind that they are human, and they are allowed to move on with their lives if they want to.


Thank you for reading my long ass rant/ TedTalk™️.
